## Quick start
- Fork the repository: https://github.com/VoxDroid/demo
- Create a branch for your change: `git checkout -b feature/your-change`
- Run tests locally and add tests for new behavior: `python -m pytest -q`
- Open a pull request with a clear description, test steps, and related issue links.

## Templates & CI
- When adding or modifying templates, include `ci_metadata.json` to help CI validate render-time placeholders.
- Use `scripts/ci_validate_templates.py` in CI to validate templates and manifests.

## Code style
- Follow PEP 8 and keep changes small and focused.
- Add tests (unit and snapshot tests for templates when appropriate).

